values:
The most memorable day of my life is when i get a new least of life.i'm saying it because my family and i have move into a new house at yishun.

The new house that my mum bought was a four room flat a bit bigger then the previous house.At last in the new house i've my own room and privacy to myself, i no longer have to share my room with my sister and mum.They now have a room each to themself. In the new house

Total defence day,is a day when all students have to  sacrifice their recess.They only can have a bun and a bottle of NEWATER.

When in class all the fans have to be switch off it was such a hot day but the teachers insisted that all the fans must be switch off.we also practice fire drills the alarm will suddenly be activated and we have to quickly line up outside the class and go to the parade square to line up.we alo need not to bring anything down as it will be very difficult for all the students and teachers.At the parade square our form teacher will take down our attendance to see if everybody is present.

After a long day at school it finally end ahh it was such a relive becauce we could finally go home and switch on the fan!! but the overall feeling on Total Defence Day was fun as we get to experince the day when war started.

Hi my name is Indah Suryana i like to do many things in my life.I like to go shoppings,and do many outdoor actvities such as rock climbing,flying fox and many more fun things.

During my free times i like to spent most of my time with my family.I will help my mum with the house chores or help my siblings with their homeworks.I also like to play wiyh my little kitten Lucy she's a very cute little kitten and she is such a dear to me because it is a gift from my late grandmother.

THE overall things about myself is i just LOVE to spent my life just the way i like it!!!
